<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <title>Registration Confirmation</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Registration Confirmation</h1>
        <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
        <p>Thank you for registering with our website. Your account has been successfully created.</p>
        <p>Please click on the following link to activate your account:</p>
        <p><a href="{{activationLink}}">{{activationLink}}</a></p>
        <p>This link will expire in {{expirationTime}}.</p>
        <p>If you did not register with our website, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>The {{appName}} Team</p>
    </body>
</html>
